articles.description: Pop superstar Harry Styles turned heads when his history-making Vogue cover was released earlier this month and it’s since become so popular its publisher has ordered a second print run.
articles.content:
Harry Styles history-making Vogue cover has proven so popular theres now a waitlist to get your hands on a copy.
